   <text:p text:style-name="P19">SPTARUL<text:note text:id="ftn32" text:note-class="footnote"><text:note-citation>32</text:note-citation><text:note-body>
      <text:p text:style-name="First_20_paragraph"><text:span text:style-name="T8">Sptar</text:span> - Dregtor la curtea domneasc care purta la ceremonii sabia i buzduganul domnului, iar mai trziu avea comanda cavaleriei. (sursa: DEX &apos;98)</text:p></text:note-body></text:note> HRAN</text:p>
