      <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"><text:span text:style-name="T8">Biv-vel</text:span> (sau <text:span text:style-name="T8">bivel</text:span>) - naintea unui titlu de dregtor (ex. <text:span text:style-name="T8">logoft</text:span>), nseamn <text:span text:style-name="T8">fost mare</text:span> dregtor de acel tip: <text:span text:style-name="T8">biv</text:span> = <text:span text:style-name="T8">fost</text:span> iar <text:span text:style-name="T8">vel</text:span> = <text:span text:style-name="T8">mare</text:span> n slavon cf. DEX &apos;98.</text:p></text:note-body></text:note>-LOGOFTUL ISAC</text:p>
