      <text:p text:style-name="First_20_paragraph"><text:span text:style-name="T8">Pan</text:span> - Denumire dat (n evul mediu) nobililor polonezi sau, prin generalizare, marilor boieri romni. (sursa: DEX &apos;98)</text:p></text:note-body></text:note> CRASNA</text:p>
